data.description: This well priced townhome in the heart of North Beach is ready for new owners. You are walking distance to all the amenities that make this beach town so desirable. You have the boardwalk, beach, shops/boutiques, dining, water park, trails, and so much more. All while being in the perfect range for commuting to DC, Andrew’s Air Force Base, Annapolis and even VA. This gem has 3 finished levels and offers quite a few upgrades including newer kitchen appliances, flooring, bathroom features and more. All three bedrooms are located on the upper floor. The primary suite boasts tall ceilings and has its own private attached bathroom . Prior owners conveniently relocated the washer and dryer from the bottom level up to the primary bedroom, so laundry can be done on the same level as the bedrooms. The middle floor has a great open concept. The kitchen has a breakfast bar area that’s open to the dining room. There is a sliding glass door off the kitchen for future deck expansion into the fenced in back yard. The floor plan then flows into the living room with a lovely bay window overlooking the community. Headed back down to the main level you will find a cute nook by the front door perfect for sitting in while taking off your shoes and then hanging up your jackets. Half of the garage was converted into a finished walk in closet for the family room/4th bedroom. It makes for great storage or even a small home office. With the additional closet and half bathroom off the family room you can easily use this as a 4th bedroom like the current owners do. This is a great price for this home and location. Make this your holiday gift to yourself!
